extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p Welcome to Whats-App, we're glad to have you 🎉🙏
  p We're still just one more step to have the ultimate experience with your friend so buckle up 😎😎😎
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody(align='center')
      tr
        td
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  div(id="digit-group" style="display: flex; align-items: center;") 
                    each val in otpCode
                      div=val
                  p(style="color:#1bd741; margin-top:20px;") Verify is Valid for 5 min
  p If you need any help with your account, please don't hesitate to contact me!
  p - Achraf Elhamzaoui, CEO
  p(style="font-size:.7rem; color:#646464;") If you didn't do this action please ignore this message